Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/s:9MiniPed.name: minLabelFont
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/s:9MiniPed.abstract: The font of the minimum value text label. If not set, the default is system font size 12.0.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/s:9MiniPed.abstract: The font of the maximum value text label. If not set, the default is system font size 12.0.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/s:9MiniPed.name: numberFormatter
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/s:9MiniPed.abstract: Each handle in the slider has a label above it showing the current selected value. By default, this is displayed as a decimal format.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: hideLabels
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: Hides the labels above the slider controls. true = labels will be hidden. false = labels will be shown. Default is false.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: labelsFixed
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: fixes the labels above the slider controls. true: labels will be fixed to both ends. false: labels will move with the handles. Default is false.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: minDistance
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: The minimum distance the two selected slider values must be apart. Default is 0.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: maxDistance
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: The maximum distance the two selected slider values must be apart. Default is CGFloat.greatestFiniteMagnitude.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: minLabelColor
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: The color of the minimum value text label. If not set, the default is the tintColor.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: maxLabelColor
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: The color of the maximum value text label. If not set, the default is the tintColor.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: handleColor
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: Handle slider with custom color, you can set custom color for your handle

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: handleBorderColor
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: Handle slider with custom border color, you can set custom border color for your handle

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: The color of the entire slider when the handle is set to the minimum value and the maximum value. Default is nil.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: disableRange
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: If true, the control will mimic a normal slider and have only one handle rather than a range.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: If true the control will snap to point at each step between minValue and maxValue. Default is false.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: step
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: The step value, this control the value of each step. If not set the default is 0.0.

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: handleImage
Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.abstract: Handle slider with custom image, you can set custom image for your handle

Classes/RangeSeekSlider.html#/c:@M@MiniP.name: handleBorderWidth
